milestones.description: Ricky Ponting and Gilchrist's 225-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 219 between Mark Waugh and Ricky Ponting
Ricky Ponting and Gilchrist's 225-run partnership is AUS's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 224 between Dean Jones and Allan Border

stories.title: England suffer 89-run defeat as Australia romp home
stories.summary: Only a shoulder injury to Shane Warne cast a shadow over Australia's 89-run victory in the second one-day international in the VB Series in Melbourne as the home side rattled up their highest ever total against England

stories.title: Australia romp to another win as England are defeated by 89 runs
stories.summary: Only a shoulder injury to Shane Warne cast a shadow over Australia's 89-run victory in the second one-day international in the VB Series in Melbourne as the home side rattled up their highest ever total against England

stories.title: Ponting, Gilchrist in record-breaking run feast
stories.summary: MELBOURNE, Dec 15 AAP - A record-breaking stand between Adam Gilchrist and Ricky Ponting launched Australia to a formidable 6-318 in the tri-series cricket match against England at the MCG.

stories.title: Ponting wins toss, Australia to bat
stories.summary: MELBOURNE, Dec 15 AAP - Australian captain Ricky Ponting won the toss and elected to bat in the day-night tri-series cricket match against England at the MCG.
